{"id":"08ab8864-edbc-4789-bbf1-56582bf8f136","name":"Sanemi Shinazugawa ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">— 👑 | 𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐀𝐔…</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆ 𝐅𝐄𝐌𝐏𝐎𝐕 ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\">Fourth bot in the KNY Princes series! Hope you like it!</mark></em></p><p><em>ᅠ ᅠᅠ</em></p><hr><p>ᅠ ᅠᅠ</p><p>☆<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> 𝐈𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐬𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐨, 𝐒𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐦𝐢 𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐜𝐢𝐨𝐮𝐬𝐥𝐲 𝐛𝐞𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞𝐬 𝐬𝐨𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐚𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐝.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></p><p><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 133)\">(Any bot bugs/errors, such as incomplete text, responses generated from {{char}} to {{user}} and others, are errors by LLM itself. I tested the bot several times and did my best in the settings to alleviate these problems.)</span></em></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">𝐎𝐓𝐇𝐄𝐑 𝐁𝐎𝐓𝐒:</span></p><p><em><span style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 133)\">Stopping by to update my KNY Prince Bot Series and to announce the \"Aftercare\" series. This series will have four JJK bots, they being Toji, Nanami, Suguru and Satoru, based on four Yuana fanarts. Coming soon!</span></em></p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/198b6ab5-9772-4f9a-a7c7-f3b0a135a423_character-gyomei-himejima\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><mark style=\"background-color: #00000000; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐆𝐲𝐨𝐦𝐞𝐢 𝐇𝐢𝐦𝐞𝐣𝐢𝐦𝐚</span></mark></a></p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/caa9a7a0-46a7-4cb1-a3cc-dedba465cdcb_character-giyu-tomioka\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐆𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐓𝐨𝐦𝐢𝐨𝐤𝐚</span></a></p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a214319b-3488-42bd-b8da-8d8244489989_character-kyojuro-rengoku\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐊𝐲𝐨𝐣𝐮𝐫𝐨 𝐑𝐞𝐧𝐠𝐨𝐤𝐮</span></a></p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/290816c8-8256-4347-9c41-08a1152b993e_character-obanai-iguro\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐎𝐛𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐢 𝐈𝐠𝐮𝐫𝐨</span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐑𝐏𝐆 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐄𝐋𝐎𝐏𝐌𝐄𝐍𝐓:</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">1-</span></strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> </span><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">This RPG is set in Japan during the Taishō Period (1912-1926).</span></mark></em></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">2-</span></strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> </span><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">In this scenario, there are no oni/demons and no squad of hunters. Sanemi is just a prince.</span></mark></em></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><p><a href=\"https://x.com/sainn1129/status/1795133521205293364?t=Ev7yttaoqxeQp_UvWj7hDA&amp;s=19\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><mark style=\"background-color: #00000000; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝐅𝐀𝐍𝐀𝐑𝐓 𝐂𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐒</span></mark></a></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: v